(2259, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Phrasal verbs 2', '#f7b211', '#18 | Spring Cleaning', 'Every spring she sorts out her clothes to decide which ones to keep.', 'Toda primavera, ela organiza as roupas dela para decidir quais guardar.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
